text: Kitchee Sports Club () is a Hong Kong sports club best known for its football team. Their home stadium is Mong Kok Stadium. ==Honours== ===Domestic=== * Hong Kong Premier League Winners (6): 2014–15, 2016–17, 2017–18, 2019–20, 2020–21, 2022–23 Runners-up (1): 2015–16 *Hong Kong First Division League Winners (6): 1947–48, 1949–50, 1963–64, 2010–11, 2011–12, 2013–14 Runners-up (7): 1952–53, 1954–55, 1956–57, 2003–04, 2006–07, 2008–09, 2012–13 *Hong Kong Senior Challenge Shield Winners (8): 1949–50, 1953–54, 1959–60, 1963–64, 2005–06, 2016–17, 2018–19, 2022–23 Finalists (6): 1948–49, 1951–52, 1955–56, 2007–08, 2009–10, 2014–15 * Hong Kong Sapling Cup Winners (2): 2017–18, 2019–20 * Hong Kong FA Cup Winners (7): 2011–12, 2012–13, 2014–15, 2016–17, 2017–18, 2018–19, 2022–23 Finalists (2): 2003–04, 2013–14 * Hong Kong League Cup Winners (5): 2005–06, 2006–07, 2011–12, 2014–15, 2015–16 * Hong Kong Junior Challenge Shield Winners (2): 1951–52, 1998–99 * Hong Kong Community Shield Winners (1): 2009 * Hong Kong Community Cup Winners (2): 2017, 2018 Finalists (3): 2014, 2015, 2016 * Hong Kong Season Play-off Winners (2): 2012–13, 2015–16 Category:Sports clubs Category:Organisations based in Hong Kong
title: Kitchee S.C.
